						<p>Stone built into a platform inside the compound of the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadaśiva.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 14[76], Ānanda, Chaitra [ba. 7], Thursday.</hi> Irregular.</p>						

						<p>Mentions Mutira Bhatimayya, son of Goparāju. Other details are lost.</p>						

